object.customQuery:
SELECT Application_Stg.SystemId, 
Application_Stg.Id,
Application_Stg.UpdateTimestamp, Application_Stg.ApplicationNumber, Application_Stg.CustomerRef, Application_Stg.PolicyRef, Application_Stg.Status, Application_Stg.TypeCd, Application_Stg.Description, basicpolicyapp_stg.PolicyNumber, case when len(basicpolicyapp_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',basicpolicyapp_stg.policyversion)
             when len(basicpolicyapp_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',basicpolicyapp_stg.policyversion)
             else basicpolicyapp_stg.policyversion end as policyversion
FROM
 dbo.Application_Stg, dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg
Where  Application_Stg.SystemId= basicpolicyapp_stg.SystemId
and Application_Stg.applicationnumber not like '%QT%'
